&lt;p&gt;The recruitment team at Myticas is currently seeking an experienced Optical Networking resource who would be interested in working within the CIP vertical. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are looking for a candidate who is currently based in Canada since this is offered on a remote full-time permanent basis and requires the resource to be located within the country.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The candidate in this role should have the following requirements:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Highly experienced in CIP Optical Networking Deployment
        &lt;li&gt;Over 8 Years of Optical Networking expertise
        &lt;li&gt;Experience with Optical Network deployment and system development
        &lt;li&gt;Experience with Optical PLM
        &lt;li&gt;Experience with Operational Support Systems
        &lt;li&gt;Experience with Open Standards and Concepts
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a &lt;strong&gt;Network Verification &amp; Test Engineer&lt;/strong&gt; to validate the performance, reliability, and compliance of advanced networking systems. This role involves creating verification plans, executing system-level tests, automating configurations, and working with industry-standard traffic generation tools. The ideal candidate will bring a strong networking background, hands-on testing expertise, and the ability to work both independently and in collaborative team settings.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Develop &lt;strong&gt;system and subsystem verification matrices&lt;/strong&gt; to ensure full coverage of all system requirements.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Coordinate and participate in &lt;strong&gt;system-level testing activities&lt;/strong&gt;, including planning, execution, and reporting of results.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Design, develop, and maintain &lt;strong&gt;test cases&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;test beds&lt;/strong&gt; to support various testing scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Execute tests using traffic generators (e.g., Spirent, IXIA, Test Center), packet capture tools (tcpdump), and performance tools (iPerf).&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Validate networking features and performance across &lt;strong&gt;OSI layers&lt;/strong&gt;, including TCP, UDP, IP networking, routing protocols, and network optimization techniques.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Implement and manage &lt;strong&gt;NETCONF&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;gRPC/gNMI&lt;/strong&gt; for automated network device configuration.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Work with structured &lt;strong&gt;data formats&lt;/strong&gt; such as JSON, JSON IETF, XML, YAML, PROTO, and &lt;strong&gt;REST APIs&lt;/strong&gt; to support automation workflows.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Utilize &lt;strong&gt;Kubernetes (POD)&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Docker&lt;/strong&gt; containers for test environment setup and management.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve performance and functional issues, ensuring timely defect identification and resolution.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Proven experience with &lt;strong&gt;traffic generation and analysis tools&lt;/strong&gt; such as Spirent, IXIA, Test Center, tcpdump, and iPerf.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Strong understanding of &lt;strong&gt;networking fundamentals&lt;/strong&gt;, including OSI layers, TCP/UDP/IP protocols, routing protocols, and optimization methods.&lt;/p&gt;

        &lt;li&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;Experience configuring and automating network devices using &lt;strong&gt;NETCONF&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;gRPC/gNMI&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

