        &lt;p&gt;Prior experience in &lt;strong&gt;network verification&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;system integration testing&lt;/strong&gt;, or &lt;strong&gt;telecom/network equipment validation&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

