&lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;Requires a BS and MS in Science or Engineering; a Doctorate in a related topic and/or a PE License is desirable.
        &lt;li&gt;Proven proficiency with the given disciplines of the position and experience with utility boilers, industrial furnaces and related equipment is essential.
        &lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="background-color: rgb(241,196,15);"&gt;Requires a minimum of 10 years of demonstrated SNCR, SCR, or water treatment experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.
